1. *Pića* su ukusna i lako se piju. (The drinks are tasty and easy to drink.)
2. On voli doručkovaću uz *piće*. (He likes to have breakfast with a drink.)
3. *Piće* nam je uvijek bilo dostupno. (The drink was always available to us.)
4. Ona je popila jedno *piće*. (She had a drink.)
5. Prošlo je puno vremena od kad sam posljednji put popio *pića*. (It has been a long time since I had a drink.)
6. Svi su se okupili u kafiću da popiju *pića*. (Everyone gathered at the cafe to have a drink.)